{"tid":451237,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"30-31/1魚蛋結案陳詞","createTime":"2017-10-29T04:03:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-30T15:26:27.000Z","uid":47359,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"03f8604e5c698835d4beb60edcd04b35b84cb1bf","tid":451237,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T04:03:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sparkalliancehk/posts/2071080473179074\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsparkalliancehk%2Fposts%2F2071080473179074&d=8xutqi624SFAlsajlE7BQnadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=50510712\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sparkalliancehk/posts/2071080473179074</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/29/120127_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F29%2F120127_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c85657ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【初一義士結案陳詞，呼籲各方到場聲援】<br />\n<br />\n十月三十日（星期一）及三十一日（星期二）上午十點正，於旺角騷亂中被控暴動罪的十位義士將於西九龍裁判法院四號庭（三樓）進行辯方結案陳詞。本平台懇請各方同道，到場聲援及保護義士出入。<br />\n<br />\n經歷漫長的審訊，他們極需同道們的支持及關注。一年多以來為著從不間斷的警署報到與審訊，身心都已遭受嚴酷的考驗；在審訊的最後兩天，他們都需要大家到場支持與鼓勵。<br />\n<br />\n計劃到場聲援的同道請自行帶備雨傘、外套、口罩及帽等，以保障自身及義士私隱。<br />\n<br />\n祝願義士一切平安，公義與我們同在。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br />\n個人簽名 &times;按此隱藏<br />\n------------------------------------<br />\nOct 28近期活躍五毛<br />\n0群龍共舞 1天才小釣手 2三色貓 3JR 4法國佬巫斯義 <br />\n5吾系甘開心牙 6真律師何君堯 7蘇麗珊 8十卜ching <br />\n9D_wade 10RedBaron 11優美開始 12阿古路 13Romanov <br />\n14返六日唔撚易 15優美開始 16民國復興 17dewi <br />\n18侵b 19曼聯明叔 20bb chu 21小翁翁</span>"},{"pid":"9f75b16bf4dce4495098fec48933d1975b7fa818","tid":451237,"uid":47359,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T04:04:52.000Z","msg":"各位記得<br />\n唔好用八仔<br />\n亦都唔好用支付寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36c116111e88ad99c257c47be8ae16f07b21de34","tid":451237,"uid":22858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T04:08:48.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母連狗尼住個仆街冚家鏟，以為搬鳩曬啲post去站務台就解決咗個問題。五毛根本係時事台災難，佢哋撚會搞其它台咩，所以反五毛唔柒係會員糾紛呀戇鳩。鴕鳥政策轉移視線正正突顯荒謬，實際上你係同流合污狼狽為奸！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb66af85d77db47f3859beb8faeb8e25b711ea99","tid":451237,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T04:10:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">祝佢地大步檻過<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"6dd04cd344ddfda5797038e8d15406f70da4b38e","tid":451237,"uid":61463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T04:12:24.000Z","msg":"唔好有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdb58bc4d34df34bd9e51f5708526f577f9a245f","tid":451237,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T04:13:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8fd1e3ce747ad96a34a7d62b8c92a85e07fa11c","tid":451237,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T04:19:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">敬義士</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a0b036a11bab9c06b24d6c0ca2a212d3dc1e96b","tid":451237,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T04:55:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deeef590a036a08e2eafe7fcb8052ca5a4402c47","tid":451237,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T05:06:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dbd407a3e0343fd285db638b11306ef69510b72","tid":451237,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T05:36:05.000Z","msg":"2016年農曆新年旺角騷亂，亦稱旺角衝突、旺角事件、旺角大衝突、旺角暴亂、旺角暴動、魚蛋革命、魚蛋騷亂、丙申旺角事變、丙申起義等，是一場在2016年2月8日（農曆正月初一）晚上至2月9日早上於香港旺角發生的警民衝突事件。"},{"pid":"c932716144399b507869386a1be835b6e5bd73d7","tid":451237,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T05:36:48.000Z","msg":"政府方面表示，事件的起因是食物環境衛生署（食環署）於新年巡邏期間被圍堵、辱罵及衝擊，需要警方協助；而有不少報導指起因是食環署因為取締新年出現的無牌熟食小販，與在場人士發生衝突，因而向警方求助。"},{"pid":"0edaca140dc9b9e45950a29d9a017247eb2491d3","tid":451237,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T05:37:46.000Z","msg":"起初只有小規模衝突，後來警隊移來高台準備實施人群管制時，人群開始堵塞馬路並與警方發生推撞。警方之後動用胡椒噴霧及警棍驅散人群，而示威者開始使用木板、磚頭、火種、玻璃瓶、垃圾桶等雜物襲擊警方，並縱火焚燒雜物阻擋警察推進，有記者被示威者襲擊，有觀點將示威者和警察分別稱呼為「暴徒」和「黑警」。有警員為保護同袍，兩度向天鳴槍示警，並擎槍指向示威者，更激發示威者更大的對抗，衝突升級。事件造成警員、記者和示威者等多人受傷，數十名示威者被警方拘捕。最高峰時有700多名示威者結集，逾2,000塊地磚被撬。事件到2月9日早上八時後人群逐漸散去才落幕。香港中聯辦、香港特區政府、建制派將本次事件定性為暴亂，而香港民主派則意見不一，但偏向譴責政府和警察造成是次事件發生。香港法院亦將本次事件定性為暴動，多位參與行動的示威者被判暴動罪成，部分被判囚，部分正候判。"},{"pid":"c1ff71d02dcae0585d60941dbe30c37e2a3b9894","tid":451237,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T05:38:05.000Z","msg":"source wikipedia"},{"pid":"6580a3d288c02634f39738c1a833f6baa881ab97","tid":451237,"uid":61463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T05:56:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c42d3324d3c4ce9691322bc89d93f4e2877b27c","tid":451237,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T06:00:22.000Z","msg":"登佢地慘<br />\n俾政棍利用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6b07ca6cee3e215e7f6028a95f5441a6feabaf7","tid":451237,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T07:24:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1beebb64f4eee506a54c2baebae16dca0097efde","tid":451237,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T07:26:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>登佢地慘<br />\n俾政棍利用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n梁天琦冇俾人拉?<br />\n黃之鋒冇俾人拉?<br />\n<br />\n五毛你都俾中國利用做condom啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58d1283df6733a1561ebb440c101e2f0acfb0fd0","tid":451237,"uid":37733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T09:24:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>登佢地慘<br />\n俾政棍利用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n梁天琦冇俾人拉?<br />\n黃之鋒冇俾人拉?<br />\n<br />\n五毛你都俾中國利用做condom啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢地俾人拉唔代表其他人唔係俾人利用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ff89d037e8f7dfba69ff1fc794bc2236fff7e3e","tid":451237,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T15:45:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gi